@NODE Main "GuidePrefs guide"

    Welcome to the GuidePrefs AmigaGuide« !
   This convenient database doc provides some information about the
   AmigaGuide« Preferences Editor by Quadra Development.

   Chapters in this guide:

   @{" Introduction " LINK Intro}
     
   @{" Menus " LINK Menus}

   @{" GuidePrefs window " LINK AGPWindow}

   @{" Tech Info " LINK TechInfo}

   @{" Credits " LINK Credits}
@ENDNODE

